            "title": "<p><img src=\"https://minio.liankexue.cn/npsc-common-bucket/default/2026-02-05/8707651894895665152.png\"></p><p><img src=\"https://minio.liankexue.cn/npsc-common-bucket/default/2026-02-05/8707651920187301888.png\"></p>",
            "referenceAnswer": "",
            "analyzeContent": "<pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\">H = int(input()) #矩形高度，编号1-H \nW = int(input()) #矩形宽度，编号1-W \nx = int(input()) #特别常数 \n\nans = 0 \n\n#遍历每一个格子，求出(r^2 + c^2)的平方根，与x + r - c进行比较 \nfor r in range(1, H + 1): \n\tfor c in range(1, W + 1): \n\t\tif ((r * r + c * c) ** 0.5) &lt;= x + r - c: \n\t\t\tans += 1 \nprint(ans)\n</pre>",
